$$ t_{i} {\text{ }} = {\text{ }}t{\text{ }} + {\text{ age}}_{i} t_{a} $$\end{document} where t is the population baseline threshold (for individuals of age zero), ta models the regression of the threshold on age, and ageiis the age in years of the individual i at assessment (Neale et al. 2006).
